      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. the ginger sounds okay, but i'm really struggling to even stand up straight right now. should i be worried about the pain moving to the side? i'm just really tired and want to sleep. if i take the ibuprofen now, will that help enough that i don't have to go to the clinic in the middle of the night? i really don't want to deal with a hospital visit if it's just bad indigestion.",
